{
  "stem": "15694.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And at first, they could hear now voices saying, if it doesn't-- if it doesn't get worse-- in Yiddish, actually-- one can survive it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Or one-- one can take it, rather, is the better translation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But it did, of course, get worse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had to leave our flat soon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Ah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now I have to go back a little bit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Before the war started, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Jewish organizations send us to a place called Zakopane.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And when I was about 10 years old-- yeah, about nine or 10 years old-- I had a very, very strong cough, and my lung-- my-- my lung was weakened.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this particular spa was very good for-- because it was in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The air for those who suffered like I did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when the time came and the youngsters went home, a group of youngsters, I could stay a bit longer.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My parents managed for me to stay a bit longer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And in those days, I met-- I met-- I met two other youngsters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "One of them could have changed my life, and the other one in a way did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The girl could have changed my life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "She was a banker's daughter, and they were going to emigrate to America.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She introduced me to her parents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I said-- if I want to come along.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Of course, I was a youngster.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I couldn't decide that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And if I had, well, my life would have been different.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "At the same time, coming to think of it, it was at that time three weeks before the beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I wonder if they got away in time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Anyway, the other person I met was a Polish young fellow, [?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
